The '''Hardangervidda Natursenter''' (Nature Centre) is a [[museum]] and [[visitor center]] of the [[Hardangervidda National Park]] in [[Norway]]. This centre is located in the village of [[Øvre Eidfjord]] in the municipality of [[Eidfjord]] in [[Hordaland]] county.
